Name: Cohort Graduation Rate (4-Year) 1
Expression:
VAR SelectedYear =
    IF(
        HASONEVALUE(Year_Definition[yr_cde]),
        VALUE(SELECTEDVALUE(Year_Definition[yr_cde])),
        BLANK()
    )

RETURN
IF(
    NOT(ISBLANK(SelectedYear)),

    VAR AllCohortStudents =
        CALCULATE(
            DISTINCTCOUNT(j1_degree_history[ID_NUM]),
            YEAR(j1_degree_history[ENTRY_DTE]) = SelectedYear,
            ALLEXCEPT(Year_Definition, Year_Definition[yr_cde])
        )

    VAR GraduatedIn4Years =
        CALCULATE(
            DISTINCTCOUNT(j1_degree_history[ID_NUM]),
            YEAR(j1_degree_history[ENTRY_DTE]) = SelectedYear,
            NOT(ISBLANK(j1_degree_history[DTE_DEGR_CONFERRED])),
            YEAR(j1_degree_history[DTE_DEGR_CONFERRED]) >= SelectedYear,
            YEAR(j1_degree_history[DTE_DEGR_CONFERRED]) <= SelectedYear + 4,
            ALLEXCEPT(Year_Definition, Year_Definition[yr_cde])
        )

    RETURN DIVIDE(GraduatedIn4Years, AllCohortStudents, 0),

    BLANK()
)

Name: Average Housing Cost Per Student
Expression:
DIVIDE(
      CALCULATE(SUM(Fees[FEES_AMT]), Fees[Revenue Category] = Room & Board")

Name: Average Time to Degree Years
Expression:
AVERAGEX(
      FILTER(
          j1_degree_history,
          NOT(ISBLANK(j1_degree_history[ENTRY_DTE])) &&
          NOT(ISBLANK(j1_degree_history[DTE_DEGR_CONFERRED]))
      ),
      DATEDIFF(
          j1_degree_history[ENTRY_DTE],
          j1_degree_history[DTE_DEGR_CONFERRED],
          DAY
      )
  ) / 365

Name: Term-to-Term Persistence Rate
Expression:
VAR CurrentTermStudents = VALUES(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM])
VAR CurrentYear = MAX(stud_term_sum_div[yr_cde])
VAR CurrentTerm = MAX(stud_term_sum_div[TRM_CDE])
VAR PreviousTermStudents = CALCULATETABLE(VALUES(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]), FILTER(ALL(stud_term_sum_div), (stud_term_sum_div[yr_cde] = CurrentYear && stud_term_sum_div[TRM_CDE] < CurrentTerm) || stud_term_sum_div[yr_cde] = CurrentYear - 1))
VAR PersistedStudents = COUNTROWS(INTERSECT(CurrentTermStudents, PreviousTermStudents))
VAR PreviousTermCount = COUNTROWS(PreviousTermStudents)
RETURN DIVIDE(PersistedStudents, PreviousTermCount, 0)

Name: Cohort Graduation Rate (4-Year)
Expression:
IF (
    HASONEVALUE ( Year_Definition[yr_cde] ),
    VAR CohortYearNum =
        VALUE ( SELECTEDVALUE ( Year_Definition[yr_cde] ) )

    -- All students who entered in the selected year
    VAR CohortStudents =
        CALCULATETABLE (
            VALUES ( j1_degree_history[ID_NUM] ),
            YEAR ( j1_degree_history[ENTRY_DTE] ) = CohortYearNum
        )

    -- Students who graduated (EXIT_DTE not blank) within 4 years of entry
    VAR GraduatedWithin4Years =
        CALCULATETABLE (
            VALUES ( j1_degree_history[ID_NUM] ),
            CohortStudents,
            NOT ISBLANK ( j1_degree_history[EXIT_DTE] ),
            YEAR ( j1_degree_history[EXIT_DTE] ) <= CohortYearNum + 4
        )

    VAR CohortSize = COUNTROWS ( CohortStudents )
    VAR GraduatedCount = COUNTROWS ( GraduatedWithin4Years )

    RETURN
        IF ( CohortSize = 0, BLANK (), DIVIDE ( GraduatedCount, CohortSize ) ),
    BLANK ()
)

Name: Fall-to-Fall Retention Rate
Expression:
VAR SelectedYear = SELECTEDVALUE(stud_term_sum_div[yr_cde], MAX(stud_term_sum_div[yr_cde]))
  VAR CurrentYear = SelectedYear
  VAR PrevYear = CurrentYear - 1
  VAR FallTerm = 10

  VAR PrevFallStudents =
      CALCULATETABLE(
          VALUES(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]),
          ALL(stud_term_sum_div),
          stud_term_sum_div[yr_cde] = PrevYear,
          stud_term_sum_div[TRM_CDE] = FallTerm
      )

  VAR CurrFallStudents =
      CALCULATETABLE(
          VALUES(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]),
          ALL(stud_term_sum_div),
          stud_term_sum_div[yr_cde] = CurrentYear,
          stud_term_sum_div[TRM_CDE] = FallTerm
      )

  VAR RetainedStudents = COUNTROWS(INTERSECT(PrevFallStudents, CurrFallStudents))
  VAR PrevFallCount = COUNTROWS(PrevFallStudents)

  RETURN
  DIVIDE(RetainedStudents, PrevFallCount, BLANK())

Name: First-Year Retention Rate

VAR PrevYearFreshmen = CALCULATETABLE(VALUES(wly_ipeds[id_num]), wly_ipeds[yr_cde] = PrevYear, wly_ipeds[class_cde] = 00")
